{"root":{"data":{"id":"dj1pg3vrf0w0","created":1780722510292,"text":"单片机CMS8S5880主控","expandState":"expand","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1phcgg3600","created":1780722607321,"text":"电源电路","font-size":18,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1qzv4iln40","created":1780726879624,"text":"开关机：\nPOWER按键(S1)短按，单片机引脚P13锁存控制，输出高电平开机；\n按键长按2秒，P13低电平关断电源关机。","font-size":16,"priority":null,"progress":1},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1r7wvwl8o0","created":1780727510370,"text":"电池电量监测：开机状态时，单片机引脚P04检测ADC分压值，从而检测电池电量","font-size":16,"progress":2},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1phcykczc0","created":1780722608417,"text":"测量电路","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dj1sglgemy80","created":1780731011875,"text":"单片机引脚P22连接74HC4060D","progress":1,"font-size":16},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dj1phdrt7n40","created":1780722610185,"text":"人机交互模块","font-size":18},"children":[]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}